Sentencas: Dense and well-adhered CuMn1.8O4 spinel-oxide coatings were successfully deposited on Crofer 22 APU substrates by a cost-effective electrophoretic deposition technique.
Titulo: Evaluation of electrophoretically deposited CuMn1.8O4 spinel coatings on Crofer 22 APU for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects

Sentencas: The coatings were effective in reducing the oxidation rate of the stainless steel substrates.
Titulo: Evaluation of electrophoretically deposited CuMn1.8O4 spinel coatings on Crofer 22 APU for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects

Sentencas: A diffusion model has been developed that indicates that the coated stainless steel substrates exhibit paralinear oxidation kinetics.
Titulo: Evaluation of electrophoretically deposited CuMn1.8O4 spinel coatings on Crofer 22 APU for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects

Sentencas: The effective diffusivities in the coating and in the thermally grown oxide scale were calculated to be 2 x 10(-15) and 2.5 x 10(-16) cm(2)/s, respectively, at 800 degrees C and 5 x 10(-16) and 1.6 x 10(-17) cm(2)/s, respectively, at 750 degrees C.
Titulo: Evaluation of electrophoretically deposited CuMn1.8O4 spinel coatings on Crofer 22 APU for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects

Sentencas: The asprocessed coated sample showed only 4.6 m Omega cm(2) of area specific resistance at 800 degrees C. (c) 2008 The Electrochemical Society.
Titulo: Evaluation of electrophoretically deposited CuMn1.8O4 spinel coatings on Crofer 22 APU for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects
